[RULES]
RULE TSRP7OPEN
IF TANK TSR_TWO LEVEL > 20
AND TANK TSR_ONE LEVEL < 10
THEN PIPE 7 STATUS IS OPEN

RULE TSRP7OPEN2
IF TANK TSR_ONE LEVEL < 5
THEN PIPE 7 STATUS IS OPEN

RULE TSRP7CLOSE1
IF TANK TSR_TWO LEVEL < 10
AND TANK TSR_ONE LEVEL > 25
THEN PIPE 7 STATUS IS CLOSED

RULE FCV1BYPASSCLOSE
IF TANK TSR_TWO LEVEL ABOVE 25
THEN PIPE FCV1BYPASS STATUS IS CLOSED

RULE FCV1BYPASSOPEN
IF TANK TSR_TWO LEVEL BELOW 5
THEN PIPE FCV1BYPASS STATUS IS OPEN

RULE PIPE8OPEN1
IF TANK BIG_ISR LEVEL > 25
AND TANK SMALL_ISR LEVEL < 20
THEN PIPE 8 STATUS IS OPEN

RULE PIPE8OPEN2
IF TANK SMALL_ISR LEVEL < 9
THEN PIPE 8 STATUS IS OPEN

RULE PIPE8CLOSE1
IF TANK BIG_ISR LEVEL < 20
AND TANK SMALL_ISR LEVEL > 20
THEN PIPE 8 STATUS IS CLOSED

RULE PIPE15CLOSE
IF TANK BIG_ISR LEVEL ABOVE 20
THEN PIPE J9-TERMINAL STATUS IS CLOSED

